# RoiView

## release on 20240726
## description
## changes
The <code>&lt;RoiView /&gt;</code> is a special component for marking <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Region_of_interest" rel="nofollow">region of interest</a> on images. Can be used in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_vision" rel="nofollow">computer vision</a>, AI and marking <a href="https://www.edrawsoft.com/template-mall-floor-plan.html" rel="nofollow">mall floor plans</a>
